nodes.text: Milo Phipps was Human male Agent who worked for the Republic Strategic Information Service on Ord Mantell during the Cold War.

Milo was a former Senator and one-time Governor of Dantooine before the Great Galactic War; on the Cold War he operated for the SIS on Ord Mantell; he believed that the former criminal Veem Set had important information about the Mantellian Separatist Movement but Set was captured by the separatists and Milo enlisted the help of a spacer to free him from the separatist base.
